{"tid":1734056,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【理大留守學生致全港市民書】","createTime":"2019-11-18T08:44:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-18T09:05:15.000Z","uid":322648,"like":17,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"9813482190f451bc7f11a24c9ba36f90b3502b9c","tid":1734056,"uid":322648,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T08:44:42.000Z","msg":"【理大留守學生致全港市民書】<br />\n<br />\n退此一步，即無死所。<br />\n黑警攻理大第8天，我們被圍困校內，外界手足為我們萬分焦急，然而我等心境平靜坦然。<br />\n<br />\n我們用血淚守護校園免受魔警侵犯，何罪之有？而本應保護學生的校長﹑校董，卻引狼入室，親手報警要借公權力拘捕自己的學生。<br />\n<br />\n我們學生將留守到最後一刻，睜眼見證校方身為師長，如何把學子推進深淵。不自由毋寧死，同學不怕被捕與死亡，因為歷史將判我們無罪。<br />\n<br />\n２０１９／１１／１８<br />\n理大留守學生絕筆"},{"pid":"d18b9b4f9f9264ab13107f66a6baed566e46e819","tid":1734056,"uid":190078,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T08:58:24.000Z","msg":"唔好灰心, 搵地方保護自己<br />\n就算黑警入去拉人, 我覺得唔係咁易告得入"},{"pid":"6643339a60a342a55e5ee28cc1d49d1d8386dbce","tid":1734056,"uid":7484,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T08:59:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"72438382ff9a6250c5f9302c50ac642ef6369b5b","tid":1734056,"uid":124711,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T08:59:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cb531a05e2cd6c8e2e0cdbe4f163f22a551cc594","tid":1734056,"uid":32655,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T09:00:09.000Z","msg":"唔好放棄，唔好自殺<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4e2c4247cfe6107b